data.title: Paul Lawrie (29005)
data.meta_description:
Although the naming of coaches was a feature back in the late 1980's there are only two First vehicles currently names.
	
	Temsa Safari 29005 is named after golfer Paul Lawrie who have a mutual arrangement to promote each other while Enviro300 67783 is named after footballer Neil Simpson.
	
	29005 is seen with its name at King Street Depot.
